# Blink Squish
This is a replication of the "VchiBan" blink-squish effect often seen on their models. The real way to do this is to set up a lattice modifier, but here's a shortcut that should work on any model without any other set-up.

Related VNyan Discord Thread: https://discord.com/channels/714814460010823690/1374410128844914700

## Instructions
Copy the codeblock below or in the text file and import it a graph
![example image](blinksquish-example.png "Blink Squish Example")

### Block
```
VNYANGRAPH:
```
